<plot>The Pink Panther's neighbor has borrowed his hedge clippers and lawn mower but hasn't returned them. An unseen narrator tells the panther first to order the neighbor to return the things, and when that doesn't work, take harsher methods into action. At the same time, the narrator tells the neighbor to defend himself against the ruthless panther who wants to take away the gardening tools he's so deeply fond of. Accompanied by stock footage of army tanks, this gradually turns into a full-scale war between the panther and the neighbor.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?433329</url></doc>
